	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hey All,
<br />
<br />So I have a CNROM pcb but the '161 was removed long ago. What I was wondering is this CNROM without the '161 still good to use as an NROM board or is it just worthless at this point? Just wanted to check before I throw the pcb in the trash.
<br />
<br />Thanks!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
