	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You might have to rewire the CHR address lines so that Q1 and Q0 out of the 161 are in a known state (for chip enables), but yes, it should still work.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


