		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">tepples wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">You might have to rewire the CHR address lines so that Q1 and Q0 out of the 161 are in a known state (for chip enables), but yes, it should still work.</div>
<br />
<br />Can you please expand on this?

		

		</td>
